\section desc Description
Common algrithtm for  \ref RecoPackages "Reco objects".

\subsection interface Public interface
None.

\subsection modules Modules
- reco::modules::TrackMerger: merges an arbitrary number of reco::TrackCollection.
- reco::modules::MuonMerger:  merges an arbitrary number of reco::MuonCollection.
- reco::modules::ElectronMerger: merges an arbitrary number of reco::ElectronCollection.
- reco::modules::PhotonMerger: merges an arbitrary number of reco::PhotonCollection.
<br>
Examples of configuration for the merger modules is the following:
\htmlonly
<pre>
  module allTracks = TrackMerger {
    vstring src = { "tracksA", "tracksB", "tracksC" }
  }
</pre>
\endhtmlonly

